{"tid":115260,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[DC][認真]覺唔覺得joker應該做主角拍返套獨立電影？","createTime":"2017-02-10T12:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T04:47:36.000Z","uid":34701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0424b4fce169939a091be66b4c5650c1c5e59574","tid":115260,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:24:22.000Z","msg":"作為Batman入面最受歡迎嘅奸角，我覺得joker絕對有資格擔正做主角拍一套戲，而唔係做BATMAN電影入面嘅配角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事方面我想睇一套係由joker仲係普通人嗰陣講起，講下佢自身有咩經歷，慢慢令佢變成一個魅力四射嘅奸角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事可以參考返The Killing Joke<br />\n[img]://<a href=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/3/32/Killingjoke.JPG[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2F3%2F32%2FKillingjoke.JPG%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=15908c35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/3/32/Killingjoke.JPG[/img]</a><br />\n呢本漫畫就係講joker講過去，但淨係拍過動畫，如果可以有一套真人嘅電影將成個joker成魔之路拍返出嚟，真係諗起都扯扯地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過到時又要諗搵邊個做joker好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c1607d50a6162fafd94c76c4360f7279b230d8","tid":115260,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"The Killing Joke:<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://laestanteriadenuria.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/944443.jpg[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flaestanteriadenuria.files.wordpress.com%2F2013%2F12%2F944443.jpg%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=12b98608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">laestanteriadenuria.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/944443.jpg[/img]</a>"},{"pid":"3ae3054d7829aa24462e764215091cbb6b3